{"tid":1458634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌散水撚既，我都入黎道歉","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:48:25.000Z","uid":260569,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"026e56eb07ce3765f2976960dfc541044dc66fb3","tid":1458634,"uid":260569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"其實我地唔係唔散水。<br />\n係唔明點解要咁早散水。<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解傳資訊既唔FC左先，攪到大班手足恐慌咁走，又留低留守派係度，會好危險。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都明白大家都係唔想送頭，如果曾經被屌既我都同你地講聲對唔住。<br />\n<br />\n賽後檢討：<br />\n<br />\n1）請傳訊既人FC, 好似今日咁，六點幾重有一堆機落緊，唔係全場無曬旅客。有旅客又有幾萬人係機場佢唔會清到場，大家都應該明白呢點，唔需要恐慌<br />\n2）接收資訊既請停一停諗一諗，係機場係上唔到網但都請你用自己判斷力同僅有資訊（eg航班牌）去自行決定，而唔係齋聽任何人<br />\n3）聽日唔會有咁多人一點入黎，請耐心等待收工既人入黎換班/接力/加塞<br />\n4）今日無清，唔化表聽日唔會有其他玩法。請大家緊記緊記幾時都係唔送頭係第一重點。你覺得危險，可以傾可以自己走，但如果你要拎牌call曬全場走，請番番番去睇第一點。<br />\n5）機場入面係同外界隔絕，網完全上唔到。要研究有咩好d既通訊⋯⋯"},{"pid":"7c089151e66f5a39646b60a2b7f573d46581b43f","tid":1458634,"uid":260569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046e4a149dae86cc9a819f29b64df796fc052f55","tid":1458634,"uid":260569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f48abd979c504733531ff6a8717bf33326262fb","tid":1458634,"uid":260569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8825e80cdd584be9dd20fab61bff6811d454f6aa","tid":1458634,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7AT6Db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7AT6Db.png&h=b6163964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場檢討POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好需要你幫手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"8c251b87222d0cd02fa7ac0e7121b8693d4d51e6","tid":1458634,"uid":260569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"推多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03debb03c287dc5cf283c6e14a0f1aa875705648","tid":1458634,"uid":195495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c22c3d19d9248c1fdec13d1785263d7c687c0c2","tid":1458634,"uid":260569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"黑警可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donn